{"tid":1466334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"捉到一隻咁叻呀？聽日放多10隻睇你哋捉到幾多。","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:40:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:34.000Z","uid":135000,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"09e0a1984ded9d0c7c3c349561a883ff8ee16f8f","tid":1466334,"uid":135000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:40:53.000Z","msg":"屌，<br />\n成場運動變撚晒捉鬼大行動。<br />\n大家入機場嘅心態到底係為乜嘢？<br />\n<br />\n捉鬼？定揸政府春袋？<br />\n<br />\n點解林鄭捱到今日呀？因為佢真係毋忘初衷囉。<br />\n死都唔撤回，死都唔搞獨立委員會。<br />\n<br />\n我哋呢？又話核彈都唔割？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">24小時都冇就開始鬼打鬼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我知大家好心急想贏，<br />\n但你鋤dee抽到四隻dee都唔係一下掟晒出去啦下話？<br />\n<br />\n唔好再互屌啦，做咗嘅嘢返唔到轉頭，<br />\n一齊諗點樣改善好過啦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化，不割蓆，不篤灰呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"d59521d06f84d1851277102c49505a8309700d4a","tid":1466334,"uid":135000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:42:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ab32455281b058da9daa75294e88c65ee1e5fb3","tid":1466334,"uid":135000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15b02bf866bcc3cba7619a3a4f55ba62b82fad39","tid":1466334,"uid":135000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:22.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"16b93d6fb1018526ac7367ded0bea8813539c87f","tid":1466334,"uid":135000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:32.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"fd2c583e42c412a7fdecda690faef33c75b583c3","tid":1466334,"uid":135000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:47.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"ad089751cd2d5d65cee82855726e043958635fcf","tid":1466334,"uid":304663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:48.000Z","msg":"5好捉啦"},{"pid":"b9e106b87ea0f7f7b8c48fdea782647477651233","tid":1466334,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy